WorkItem.ClosedComment: Declined: Weapon DPS is not something you can stack, like Strength or Agility. There are only a couple of sources of "Weapon Damage" (a couple enchants, and they are always, always outdone by other enchants and the one trinket, which is done in the trinket chart). If you are looking to make a Pawn string, use the Pawn Export.
